summary: Today I binge-watched 6 episodes of Killing Eve and then I watched the first episode in the new series of Doctor Who and I am...
body:
Today I binge-watched 6 episodes of Killing Eve and then I watched the first episode in the new series of Doctor Who and I am totally here for all the great female performances in both shows.

Also, Jodie Whittaker portraying the Doctor as a northerner is A++++++
